&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;为视觉语言模型（VLM）配置并加载 LoRA（Low-Rank Adaptation）微调参数&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure class=&#34;highlight python&#34;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&#34;code&#34;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;model = FastVisionModel.get_peft_model(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;    model,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;    finetune_vision_layers     = &lt;span class=&#34;literal&#34;&gt;True&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&#34;comment&#34;&gt;# False if not finetuning vision layers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;    finetune_language_layers   = &lt;span class=&#34;literal&#34;&gt;True&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&#34;comment&#34;&gt;# False if not finetuning language layers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;    finetune_attention_modules = &lt;span class=&#34;literal&#34;&gt;True&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&#34;comment&#34;&gt;# False if not finetuning attention layers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;    finetune_mlp_modules       = &lt;span class=&#34;literal&#34;&gt;True&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&#34;comment&#34;&gt;# False if not finetuning MLP layers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;    r = &lt;span class=&#34;number&#34;&gt;16&lt;/span&gt;,           &lt;span class=&#34;comment&#34;&gt;# The larger, the higher the accuracy, but might overfit&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;    lora_alpha = &lt;span class=&#34;number&#34;&gt;16&lt;/span&gt;,  &lt;span class=&#34;comment&#34;&gt;# Recommended alpha == r at least&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;    lora_dropout = &lt;span class=&#34;number&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;    bias = &lt;span class=&#34;string&#34;&gt;&amp;quot;none&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;    random_state = &lt;span class=&#34;number&#34;&gt;3407&lt;/span&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;    use_rslora = &lt;span class=&#34;literal&#34;&gt;False&lt;/span&gt;,  &lt;span class=&#34;comment&#34;&gt;# We support rank stabilized LoRA&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;    loftq_config = &lt;span class=&#34;literal&#34;&gt;None&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&#34;comment&#34;&gt;# And LoftQ&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;    &lt;span class=&#34;comment&#34;&gt;# target_modules = &amp;quot;all-linear&amp;quot;, # Optional now! Can specify a list if needed&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;Unsloth: Making `model.base_model.model.model.visual` require gradients
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;数据准备&#34;&gt;数据准备&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;用LaTeX数据集微调 VL 模型, 数据集: &lt;a href=&#34;https://huggingface.co/datasets/unsloth/LaTeX_OCR&#34;&gt;unsloth/LaTeX_OCR&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure class=&#34;highlight python&#34;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&#34;code&#34;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;keyword&#34;&gt;from&lt;/span&gt; datasets &lt;span class=&#34;keyword&#34;&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; load_dataset&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;dataset = load_dataset(&lt;span class=&#34;string&#34;&gt;&amp;quot;unsloth/LaTeX_OCR&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;, split = &lt;span class=&#34;string&#34;&gt;&amp;quot;train&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;README.md:   0%|          | 0.00/519 [00:00&amp;lt;?, ?B/s]



data/train-00000-of-00001.parquet:   0%|          | 0.00/344M [00:00&amp;lt;?, ?B/s]



